node.detail_zh: 患者為印尼藉傭工，12 月回印尼，因獲新工作於 6 月 21 日回港，沒有病徵。與第 #1132 宗個案患者有關連。
node.detail_en: The patient is an Indonesia domestic helper, having returned to Indonesia in December, 2019, and came to Hong Kong in June upon a new appointment. She exhibited no symptoms and her case has epidemiological to that of patient #1132.
